  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-badge\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-badge/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 100 (A) — No issues.\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. No hardcoded values. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Semantic markup. Color contrast for all variants. Screen reader text for status badges.\n3. **Functionality** — Variants (info, success, warning, error, neutral). Sizes. Pill/dot modes. Content overflow.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. Inline/block display modes.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — Verify 100 score.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. All variants. Accessibility.\n8. **Storybook** — All variants/sizes. Interactive controls.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
